  ('CaravanStop.StopResourceName', 'en', 'Stop Resource Name', 'The name of the resource that applies to this caravan stop record. Typical stops are represented by open house or listing records. A stop might also be another custom/local resource.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/CaravanStop/StopResourceName/', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CaravanResourceName/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
