  ('Member.SourceSystemID', 'en', 'Source System ID', 'The OUID Resource''s OrganizationUniqueId of the source record provider. The source system is the system from which the record was directly received. In cases where the source system was not where the record originated (the authoritative system), see the Originating System fields.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/Member/SourceSystemID/', NULL, '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
