  ('OUID.OrganizationType', 'en', 'Organization Type', 'The type of organization (i.e., MLS, vendor, association, etc.). This is not a substitute or alternative for the Office resource; however, it may be that a brokerage has a record in this table for a nonlisting purpose.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/OUID/OrganizationType/', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/OrganizationType/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
