  ('Property.CommonInterest', 'en', 'Common Interest', 'A type of ownership in a property that is composed of an individual lot or unit and a share of the ownership or use of common areas. A Common Interest Development (CID) is usually governed by a recorded set of Covenants, Conditions & Restrictions (CC&Rs).', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/Property/CommonInterest/', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
