  ('Property.ContingentDate', 'en', 'Contingent Date', 'The date an offer was made with a contingency. The listing remains on market. This is the date entered by the agent reflecting when the change occurred contractually, not a timestamp of when the change was made in the MLS.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/Property/ContingentDate/', NULL, '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
