  ('ShowingRequest.ShowingAgentMlsId', 'en', 'Showing Agent MLS ID', 'The local, well-known identifier for the member who has scheduled to access the property, most commonly representing a buyer. This value may not be unique. Specifically, in the case of aggregation systems, this value should be the identifier from the original system.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/ShowingRequest/ShowingAgentMlsId/', NULL, '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
