  ('Appliances', 'Tankless Water Heater', 'en', 'Tankless Water Heater', 'A tankless water heater is included with the property.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/Appliances/Tankless Water Heater/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
