  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Performance Management Network / PMN', 'en', 'Performance Management Network / PMN', 'This designation is unique to the REALTOR® family of designations, emphasizing that in order to enhance your business, you must enhance yourself. It focuses on negotiating strategies and tactics, networking and referrals, business planning and systems, personal performance management, and leadership development. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/pmn', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Performance Management Network %2F PMN/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Pricing Strategy Advisor / PSA', 'en', 'Pricing Strategy Advisor / PSA', 'Enhance your skills in pricing properties, creating CMAs (comparative market analysis), working with appraisers and guiding clients through the anxieties and misperceptions they often have about home values with the National Association of REALTORS® PSA (Pricing Strategy Advisor) certification. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/psa', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Pricing Strategy Advisor %2F PSA/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'REALTOR Association Certified Executive / RCE', 'en', 'REALTOR Association Certified Executive / RCE', 'The REALTOR® Association Certified Executive (RCE) is the only professional designation designed specifically for REALTOR® association executives. RCE designees exemplify goal-oriented AEs with drive, experience and commitment to professional growth. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/rce', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/REALTOR Association Certified Executive %2F RCE/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Real Estate Negotiation Expert / RENE', 'en', 'Real Estate Negotiation Expert / RENE', 'This certification is for real estate professionals who want to sharpen their negotiation skills. The RENE certification program gives REALTORS® the tips and tools they need to be skillful advocates for their clients. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/rene', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Real Estate Negotiation Expert %2F RENE/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Residential Accredited Appraiser / RAA', 'en', 'Residential Accredited Appraiser / RAA', 'For residential appraisers, this designation is awarded to those whose education and experience exceed state appraisal certification requirements and is supported by the National Association of REALTORS®. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/raa', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Residential Accredited Appraiser %2F RAA/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Resort & Second-Home Property Specialist / RSPS', 'en', 'Resort & Second-Home Property Specialist / RSPS', 'This certification is designed for REALTORS® who facilitate the buying, selling or management of properties for investment, development, retirement or second homes in a resort, recreational and/or vacation destination. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/rsps', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Resort & Second-Home Property Specialist %2F RSPS/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Seller Representative Specialist / SRS', 'en', 'Seller Representative Specialist / SRS', 'The Seller Representative Specialist (SRS) designation is the premier credential in seller representation. It is designed to elevate professional standards and enhance personal performance. The designation is awarded by the Real Estate Business Institute (REBI) to real estate practitioners who meet specific educational and practical experience criteria. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/seller-representative-specialist-srs', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Seller Representative Specialist %2F SRS/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Seniors Real Estate Specialist / SRES', 'en', 'Seniors Real Estate Specialist / SRES', 'The Seniors Real Estate Specialist (SRES®) designation program educates REALTORS® on how to profitably and ethically serve the real estate needs of the fastest-growing market in real estate, clients age 50+. Those who earn the SRES® designation gain access to valuable member benefits, useful resources and networking opportunities across the U.S. and Canada in order to help their businesses thrive. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/sres', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Seniors Real Estate Specialist %2F SRES/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Short Sales & Foreclosure Resource / SFR', 'en', 'Short Sales & Foreclosure Resource / SFR', 'The Short Sales & Foreclosure Resource (SFR®) certification teaches real estate professionals to work with distressed sellers and the finance, tax and legal professionals who can help them. Learn how to qualify sellers for short sales, develop a short sale package, negotiate with lenders, safeguard your commission, limit risk, protect buyers and more. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/sfr', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Short Sales & Foreclosure Resource %2F SFR/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Society of Industrial and Office REALTORS / SIOR', 'en', 'Society of Industrial and Office REALTORS / SIOR', 'The Society of Industrial and Office REALTORS® (SIOR) designation is held by only the most knowledgeable, experienced and successful commercial real estate brokerage specialists. To earn it, designees must not only provide recommendations but must meet standards of experience, production, education and ethics. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/sior', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Society of Industrial and Office REALTORS %2F SIOR/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'Transnational Referral Certification / TRC', 'en', 'Transnational Referral Certification / TRC', 'Real estate professionals who have taken the Transnational Referral Certified (TRC) training, have completed special training on making and receiving client referrals from professionals in other countries. https://worldproperties.com/about-us/international-referrals-and-trc/', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/Transnational Referral Certification %2F TRC/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CoListAgentDesignation', 'e-PRO', 'en', 'e-PRO', 'The National Association of REALTORS® e-PRO® certification teaches you to use cutting-edge technologies and digital initiatives to link up with today''s savvy real estate consumer. https://www.nar.realtor/designations-and-certifications/e-pro', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CoListAgentDesignation/e-PRO/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonInterest', 'Community Apartment', 'en', 'Community Apartment', 'Ownership interest where purchaser receives a partial/fractional interest in the land coupled with the right of exclusive occupancy of an apartment located thereon. The owners elect a governing board which operates and maintains the project.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/Community Apartment/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonInterest', 'Condominium', 'en', 'Condominium', 'Ownership of an individual unit where each homeowner only owns their individual unit space and an undivided share in the ownership of common areas or in a common homeowner association (HOA). Generally, the ownership of the individual unit is described in a Condominium Plan and usually consists of ownership of the surface of the walls and the space within. The covenants, conditions and restrictions (CC&Rs) will detail what building components and other complex amenities are considered part of the common area and will describe the common area or HOA ownership percentages and maintenance responsibilities.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/Condominium/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonInterest', 'None', 'en', 'None', 'Ownership of an entire parcel or lot that is not in a common-interest development (CID) or not held subject to any other common interest rights.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/None/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonInterest', 'Planned Development', 'en', 'Planned Development', 'Ownership consisting of an individual lot or parcel, generally including the ownership of the land and any structures on the individual lot or parcel. Owners also receive use right in common areas that are generally owned by a homeowner association (HOA). Some common areas may be reserved for the use of some or all of the individual lot owners. Generally, the covenants, conditions and restrictions (CC&Rs) will detail the method of management, maintenance, use and control of the common areas and may provide for some control and maintenance of the individual lots.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/Planned Development/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonInterest', 'Stock Cooperative', 'en', 'Stock Cooperative', 'Ownership of an interest in a corporation which is formed primarily for the purpose of holding title to improved real property, either in fee simple or for a term of years. All or substantially all of the shareholders receive a right of exclusive occupancy of a portion of the real property, which right is transferable only concurrently with the transfer of the share(s) of stock in the corporation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/Stock Cooperative/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonInterest', 'Timeshare', 'en', 'Timeshare', 'Ownership in a time period or a point system granting possession rights to a unit or occupancy rights at a property. The property may be owned either by a number of individuals on a fractional basis or may be an interest in a corporation each with the right of possession for a specified time interval. Time-sharing is commonly applied to resort and vacation properties.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonInterest/Timeshare/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonWalls', '1 Common Wall', 'en', '1 Common Wall', 'The dwelling being sold has one common wall with another property that is not part of the sale. Also known as an attached structure.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonWalls/1 Common Wall/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonWalls', '2+ Common Walls', 'en', '2+ Common Walls', 'The dwelling being sold has two or more common walls with another property that is not part of the sale. Also known as an attached structure.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonWalls/2+ Common Walls/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonWalls', 'End Unit', 'en', 'End Unit', 'The dwelling being sold has one or more common walls with another property that is not part of the sale and is at the end of a row of units. Also known as an attached structure.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonWalls/End Unit/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonWalls', 'No Common Walls', 'en', 'No Common Walls', 'The dwelling being sold has no attached structures that are not part of the sale. Also know as a detached structure.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonWalls/No Common Walls/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonWalls', 'No One Above', 'en', 'No One Above', 'The property is attached to another dwelling that is not part of the sale, but there is no unit above the one being sold.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonWalls/No One Above/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommonWalls', 'No One Below', 'en', 'No One Below', 'The property is attached to another dwelling that is not part of the sale, but there is no unit below the one being sold.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommonWalls/No One Below/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Airport/Runway', 'en', 'Airport/Runway', 'The community has an airport or runway.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Airport%2FRunway/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Clubhouse', 'en', 'Clubhouse', 'The community has a clubhouse.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Clubhouse/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Curbs', 'en', 'Curbs', 'The community streets have curbs.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Curbs/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Fishing', 'en', 'Fishing', 'The community has places to go fishing.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Fishing/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Fitness Center', 'en', 'Fitness Center', 'The community has a fitness center.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Fitness Center/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Gated', 'en', 'Gated', 'The community is gated.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Gated/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Golf', 'en', 'Golf', 'The community has golfing.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Golf/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Lake', 'en', 'Lake', 'The community has a lake.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Lake/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'None', 'en', 'None', 'The community includes no additional features.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/None/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Other', 'en', 'Other', 'The community has features beyond those listed in this field.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Other/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Park', 'en', 'Park', 'The community has a park.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Park/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Pickleball', 'en', 'Pickleball', 'The community has a pickleball court.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Pickleball/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Playground', 'en', 'Playground', 'The community has a playground.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Playground/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Pool', 'en', 'Pool', 'The community has a pool.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Pool/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Racquetball', 'en', 'Racquetball', 'The community has racquetball facilities.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Racquetball/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Restaurant', 'en', 'Restaurant', 'The community has a restaurant.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Restaurant/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Sidewalks', 'en', 'Sidewalks', 'The community streets have sidewalks.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Sidewalks/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Stable(s)', 'en', 'Stable(s)', 'The community has one or more horse stables.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Stable(s)/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Street Lights', 'en', 'Street Lights', 'The community streets have lighting.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Street Lights/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Suburban', 'en', 'Suburban', 'The community is a suburban setting.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Suburban/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CommunityFeatures', 'Tennis Court(s)', 'en', 'Tennis Court(s)', 'The community has one or more tennis courts.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CommunityFeatures/Tennis Court(s)/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CompensationType', '$', 'en', '$', 'The value entered in any of the compensation fields (BuyerBrokerageCompensation, SubAgencyCompensation, TransactionBrokerCompensation) as a dollar amount of the gross compensation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CompensationType/$/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CompensationType', '%', 'en', '%', 'The value entered in any of the compensation fields (BuyerBrokerageCompensation, SubAgencyCompensation, TransactionBrokerCompensation) as a percentage of the gross compensation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CompensationType/%/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CompensationType', 'Other', 'en', 'Other', 'A compensation type not included on this list.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CompensationType/Other/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('CompensationType', 'See Remarks', 'en', 'See Remarks', 'The value entered in any of the compensation fields (BuyerBrokerageCompensation, SubAgencyCompensation, TransactionBrokerCompensation) is something other than % or $ or is a special combination of $, % and other compensation types. See the applicable remarks field for more details about the compensation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/CompensationType/See Remarks/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('Concessions', 'Call Listing Agent', 'en', 'Call Listing Agent', 'Call the listing agent for information about concessions made/offered by the seller.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/Concessions/Call Listing Agent/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('Concessions', 'No', 'en', 'No', 'There are no concessions included with this listing.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/Concessions/No/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('Concessions', 'Yes', 'en', 'Yes', 'There are concessions that are part of the listing/sale.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/Concessions/Yes/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Adobe', 'en', 'Adobe', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with adobe.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Adobe/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Aluminum Siding', 'en', 'Aluminum Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with aluminum siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Aluminum Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Asbestos', 'en', 'Asbestos', 'The structure includes asbestos as a construction material.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Asbestos/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Asphalt', 'en', 'Asphalt', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with asphalt.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Asphalt/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Attic/Crawl Hatchway(s) Insulated', 'en', 'Attic/Crawl Hatchway(s) Insulated', 'When not insulated, a home’s attic hatch or crawlspace hatch creates one of the biggest gaps in the building envelope, increasing heat loss in winter and heat gain in summer, while making indoor living areas uncomfortable. Insulation standards are clearly defined. http://www.ornl.gov/sci/roofs+walls/insulation/fact', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Attic%2FCrawl Hatchway(s) Insulated/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Batts Insulation', 'en', 'Batts Insulation', 'Rolls and batts, or blankets, are flexible products made from mineral fibers such as fiberglass, rock wool, cotton or wool. They are available in widths suited to standard spacing of wall studs and attic or floor joists.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Batts Insulation/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Block', 'en', 'Block', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with block.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Block/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Blown-In Insulation', 'en', 'Blown-In Insulation', 'Blown-in or loose-fill insulation is usually made of fiberglass, rock wool or cellulose in the form of loose fibers or fiber pellets installed using special pneumatic equipment. The blown-in material conforms readily to odd-sized building cavities and attics with wires, ducts and pipes, making it well suited for places where it is difficult to effectively install other types of insulation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Blown-In Insulation/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Board & Batten Siding', 'en', 'Board & Batten Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with board & batten siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Board & Batten Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Brick', 'en', 'Brick', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with brick.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Brick/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Brick Veneer', 'en', 'Brick Veneer', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with brick veneer.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Brick Veneer/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Cedar', 'en', 'Cedar', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with cedar.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Cedar/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Cement Siding', 'en', 'Cement Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with cement siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Cement Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Clapboard', 'en', 'Clapboard', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with clapboard.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Clapboard/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Concrete', 'en', 'Concrete', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with concrete.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Concrete/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Ducts Professionally Air-Sealed', 'en', 'Ducts Professionally Air-Sealed', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with ducts professionally air-sealed.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Ducts Professionally Air-Sealed/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Exterior Duct-Work is Insulated', 'en', 'Exterior Duct-Work is Insulated', 'U.S. Department of Energy (DOE) estimates that heating and cooling ducts located in unconditioned spaces such as attics and garages can underperform by 60-75 percent. Exterior ducts that are properly insulated can save energy and reduce overall equipment sizing. Insulation standards are clearly defined at https://www.energy.gov/energysaver/insulation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Exterior Duct-Work is Insulated/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Fiber Cement', 'en', 'Fiber Cement', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with fiber cement.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Fiber Cement/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Fiberglass Siding', 'en', 'Fiberglass Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with fiberglass siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Fiberglass Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Foam Insulation', 'en', 'Foam Insulation', 'Spray foam or foam-in-place insulation can be sprayed into walls, on attic surfaces, or under floors to insulate and reduce air leakage. There are two types of foam-in-place insulation: closed-cell and open-cell. Both are typically made with polyurethane. Closed-cell foam has a greater insulation value and provides stronger resistance against moisture and air leakage. Open-cell foam is lighter and less expensive but should not be used below ground level where it could absorb water.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Foam Insulation/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Frame', 'en', 'Frame', 'The structure includes a frame.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Frame/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Glass', 'en', 'Glass', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with glass.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Glass/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'HardiPlank Type', 'en', 'Hardi Plank Type', 'The structure includes HardiPlank® siding as a construction material.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/HardiPlank Type/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'ICAT Recessed Lighting', 'en', 'ICAT Recessed Lighting', 'ICAT (Insulation Contact Air Tight) recessed light fixtures are rated both to safely come in contact with insulation and are better airsealed. They can be installed safely with insulation and air sealing. These lights are different from IC (Insulation Contact) fixtures, which are not very airtight. They can also be identified by the wording “Washington State Approved.” Documentation on the installation is recommended because ICAT rating often requires that multiple components are used as specified by the manufacturer. Substitutions of components can negate the rating. More information can be found at http://energy.gov/energysaver/articles/tips-lighting and http://energy.gov/energysaver/articles/tips-insulation.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/ICAT Recessed Lighting/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'ICFs (Insulated Concrete Forms)', 'en', 'ICFs (Insulated Concrete Forms)', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with insulated concrete forms.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/ICFs (Insulated Concrete Forms)/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Lap Siding', 'en', 'Lap Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with lap siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Lap Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Log', 'en', 'Log', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with log.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Log/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Log Siding', 'en', 'Log Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with log siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Log Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Low VOC Insulation', 'en', 'Low VOC Insulation', 'Volatile organic compounds (VOCs) are emitted as gases from certain solids or liquids. Different types of insulation can be certified for having low VOC content by third-party verifiers such as GreenGuard.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Low VOC Insulation/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Masonite', 'en', 'Masonite', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with Masonite.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Masonite/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Metal Siding', 'en', 'Metal Siding', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with metal siding.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Metal Siding/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
  ('ConstructionMaterials', 'Natural Building', 'en', 'Natural Building', 'The structure was made wholly or partly with natural building.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/ConstructionMaterials/Natural Building/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
