  ('EventSource', 'GPS', 'en', 'GPS', 'The source of the object is the result of Global Positioning System (GPS) activity.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/EventSource/GPS/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
