  ('EventSource', 'Map', 'en', 'Map', 'The source of the object being viewed pertaining to application structure (e.g., the listing impression was displayed on a map).', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/EventSource/Map/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
