  ('InteriorOrRoomFeatures', 'Tray Ceiling(s)', 'en', 'Tray Ceiling(s)', 'A ceiling with an inverted tray or recessed area, often rectangular, that adds depth and interest.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/InteriorOrRoomFeatures/Tray Ceiling(s)/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
