  ('StructureType', 'Manufactured House', 'en', 'Manufactured House', 'A factory-built house that is transported to a lot. A manufactured home will have a serial/license number, where prefabricated (modular) homes are classified with stick built as "House" on this list.', 'https://dd.reso.org/DD2.0/lookups/StructureType/Manufactured House/', '2.0', 'reso_official_csv'),
